  "detailed_description": "Romeow is a minimalist and charming puzzle game about a kitten who is too young to find the way by itself. He is just a kitten, he feels lost when he is without his favorite toy. Go through the messy paths and take Romeow 's wool back so he can sleep in his cozy bed.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>40 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity;<br></li><li>No score, no timer and no pressure;<br></li><li>Pleasant sound track;<br></li><li>Lovely art style.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Messy paths</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527510/extras/a3fa53fb7ff19bb0f5976d65f97949d0.poster.avif?t=1728601738\" width=518 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527510/extras/a3fa53fb7ff19bb0f5976d65f97949d0.webm?t=1728601738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527510/extras/a3fa53fb7ff19bb0f5976d65f97949d0.mp4?t=1728601738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
